_aLatestUpdates._sText:
Still dissatisfied with the map, I decided to update it.

- Fixed/changed all boosters (they should now work all the time without having to shoot on them).
- Changed/removed some disliked parts of the map, it should hopefully be less annoying to play now.

_sText:
Second bunnyhop map. Medium length & difficulty.

**v2 changes**

Still dissatisfied with the map, I decided to update it.

- Fixed/changed all boosters (they should now work all the time without having to shoot on them).
- Changed/removed some disliked parts of the map, it should hopefully be less annoying to play now.

**bhop null fix changes**

- Fixed the boosters (they were unreliable and did not always work for some reason, apologies for that). You can now shoot on them for an unbreakable boost, as well as simply jumping on them like before.
- Changed some annoying/glitchy parts, nothing major.
